description: President Xi Jinping of China and Russia's Vladimir Putin doubled down on their alliance against the West this week during the Kremlin leader's visit to Beijing.
title: Putin and Xi further their embrace to defy U.S.-led pressure

description: Ckunsa, an indigenous language in Chile, was declared dead 70 years ago. But groups in northern Chile are successfully reviving the language and teaching it to a new generation.
title: Saving a Language in Chile

description: Ahead of Biden's address at Morehouse, students share their frustrations
title: Biden is set for the Morehouse graduation. Students are divided

description: The first trucks of aid entered Gaza via a pier built by the U.S. But it's challenging to move aid around Gaza, and humanitarian groups operating in Rafah warn they don't have food to distribute.
title: Rafah is running out of food, even as the U.S. pier starts operating in Gaza

description: President Biden will cap off a week of outreach to Black Americans with commencement at Morehouse College. Billie Eilish tells Morning Edition how she found herself on her newest album.
title: Biden focuses on outreach to Black Americans; Billie Eilish finds herself

description: As part of our series on "the Science of Siblings," we looked at how some brothers and sisters are best friends. Here are some of the stories you shared of close ties with siblings.
title: We asked, you answered: What's the secret to a close relationship with siblings?

description: French police shot and killed a man armed with a knife and a metal bar who is suspected of having set fire to a synagogue in the Normandy city of Rouen early on Friday, authorities said.
title: French police fatally shoot a man suspected of planning to set fire to a synagogue

description: Across the city, power lines and trees are downed, traffic lights are out and glass is scattered across downtown. About 900,000 customers were left without power early Friday.
title: At least 4 people are killed in Houston after a severe thunderstorm passed through
